## Use Cases ğŸš€
- Website hosting ğŸŒ
- Backup and archival ğŸ“‚
- Big Data analytics input/output storage ğŸ“Š
- Content delivery for media and apps ğŸ¬
- Disaster recovery storage ğŸ›¡ï¸

---

## Summary ğŸ“
- GCS is **object storage**, not block or file storage.  
- Data is stored in **buckets** and organized as **objects**.  
- Choose storage class & location based on **cost vs access frequency** âš–ï¸.  
- IAM and ACLs control access to buckets/objects ğŸ”‘.  
- GCS integrates with other GCP services like BigQuery, Dataflow, AI/ML ğŸ¤–.
